---
layout: layouts/base-finpay.njk
title: "Federal Benefits Masterclass | Weber State University"
description: "A comprehensive briefing on FERS, TSP, FEGLI, and Social Security for Northern Utah Federal Employees."
bodyClass: "landing-page"
---

<style>
/* Landing page CSS - All vanilla CSS, no Tailwind */
.sem-landing-page {
  --primary: #16253C;
  --primary-container: #16253C;
  --secondary: #C4A82A;
  --secondary-container: #ffac60;
  --surface: #f8f9fb;
  --surface-container-low: #f3f4f6;
  --on-primary: #ffffff;
  --on-primary-container: #9fc2ff;
  --on-secondary: #ffffff;
  --primary-fixed: #d5e3ff;
  --slate-600: #475569;
  --slate-700: #334155;
  --slate-500: #64748b;
  font-family: var(--font-body), -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
}

/* Hide entire site header/nav on landing page */
.landing-page .finpay-header {
  display: none !important;
  height: 0 !important;
  min-height: 0 !important;
  max-height: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  margin: 0 !important;
  overflow: hidden !important;
  visibility: hidden !important;
  position: absolute !important;
}

.landing-page .finpay-header *,
.landing-page header *,
.landing-page .finpay-nav-wrapper,
.landing-page .finpay-nav,
.landing-page .finpay-nav-links,
.landing-page .finpay-nav-right,
.landing-page .finpay-nav-logo,
.landing-page .desktop-cta,
.landing-page .client-login-cta,
.landing-page .mobile-menu-btn {
  display: none !important;
  height: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  margin: 0 !important;
}

/* Glass effect utility */
.sem-liquid-glass {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
}

/* Editorial pull quote with orange left border */
.sem-editorial-pull-quote {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 32px;
  padding-top: 16px;
  padding-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-editorial-pull-quote::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 4px;
  background-color: var(--secondary);
}

/* Hero Section */
.sem-hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-top: 0;
  padding-bottom: 80px;
  padding-left: 32px;
  padding-right: 32px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.sem-hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
}

.sem-hero-bg img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  filter: grayscale(0.2) contrast(1.1);
}

.sem-hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.9) 0%, rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.4) 50%, transparent 100%);
}

.sem-hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  width: 100%;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: center;
}

.sem-hero-left {
  color: white;
}

.sem-eyebrow {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  color: #FDD25E;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #FDD25E;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
}

.sem-hero-title {
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.sem-hero-title-accent {
  color: var(--secondary-container);
  font-style: italic;
}

.sem-hero-description {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.4;
  max-width: 600px;
  color: var(--primary-fixed);
  opacity: 0.9;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.sem-trust-stats {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 48px;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

.sem-trust-stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}

.sem-trust-stat-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--secondary-container);
}

.sem-trust-stat-value {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* Registration Form */
.sem-registration-card {
  position: relative;
}

.sem-registration-form {
  padding: 32px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}

.sem-form-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
}

.sem-limited-seating {
  background: var(--secondary);
  color: var(--on-secondary);
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-form-title {
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: #0F1A2A;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.sem-form-subtitle {
  color: var(--slate-600);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
}

.sem-form-group {
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-form-label {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.sem-form-input {
  width: 100%;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  border: none;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.1);
  padding: 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 16px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.sem-form-input::placeholder {
  color: #94a3b8;
}

.sem-form-input:focus {
  outline: none;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px var(--secondary);
}

.sem-checkbox-group {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-checkbox {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  margin-top: 2px;
  accent-color: var(--primary);
}

.sem-checkbox-label {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #374151;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.sem-submit-btn {
  width: 100%;
  background: #16253C;
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.sem-submit-btn:hover {
  background: var(--primary-container);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.sem-submit-btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.7;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  transform: none;
}

.sem-privacy-text {
  text-align: center;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--slate-500);
  margin-top: 16px;
}

/* Curriculum Section */
.sem-curriculum {
  padding: 64px 32px;
  background: var(--surface-container-low);
}

.sem-curriculum-container {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.sem-curriculum-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
  gap: 64px;
}

.sem-curriculum-sidebar h2 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.sem-curriculum-sidebar .sem-eyebrow {
  color: #FDD25E;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #FDD25E;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-pull-quote {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--slate-700);
}

.sem-curriculum-cards {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
}

.sem-curriculum-card {
  background: white;
  padding: 40px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 48px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.sem-curriculum-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.sem-chapter-number {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #57A5F4;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  opacity: 0.7;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sem-curriculum-card h4 {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-curriculum-card p {
  color: var(--slate-600);
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.sem-card-tags {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
}

.sem-card-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  background: var(--surface-container-low);
  color: var(--primary);
  border-radius: 999px;
}

/* Speaker Section */
.sem-speaker {
  padding: 64px 32px;
  background: #f8f9fb;
}

.sem-speaker-container {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 96px;
  align-items: center;
}

.sem-speaker-image-wrapper {
  position: relative;
}

.sem-speaker-image {
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
  line-height: 0;
}

.sem-speaker-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}

.sem-speaker-quote-card {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -32px;
  right: -32px;
  background: var(--primary);
  padding: 48px;
  color: white;
  z-index: 20;
  border-radius: 8px;
  max-width: 300px;
}

.sem-speaker-quote-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  opacity: 0.7;
  color: var(--on-primary-container);
}

.sem-speaker-quote {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.sem-speaker-details .sem-eyebrow {
  color: #FDD25E;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #FDD25E;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-speaker-name {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.sem-speaker-credentials {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-speaker-bio {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--slate-700);
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-credentials-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
}

.sem-credential-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 16px;
}

.sem-checkmark {
  color: var(--secondary);
  font-size: 20px;
  margin-top: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sem-credential-text {
  color: var(--slate-600);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* Venue Section */
.sem-venue {
  padding: 64px 32px;
  background: var(--surface);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.sem-venue-container {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.sem-venue-content {
  display: flex;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: stretch;
}

.sem-venue-details {
  flex: 1;
  background: white;
  padding: 48px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border-left: 8px solid var(--primary);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
}

.sem-venue-details .sem-eyebrow {
  color: #FDD25E;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #FDD25E;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-venue-title {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-venue-title-light {
  font-weight: 300;
}

.sem-venue-info {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
  color: var(--slate-600);
}

.sem-venue-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}

.sem-venue-icon {
  font-size: 20px;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
}

.sem-venue-image {
  flex: 1;
  min-height: 400px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.sem-venue-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

/* FAQ Section */
.sem-faq {
  padding: 64px 32px;
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
}

.sem-faq-container {
  max-width: 1024px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.sem-faq-title {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  margin-bottom: 64px;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.sem-faq-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 32px;
  text-align: left;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
}

.sem-faq-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-faq-question {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.sem-faq-answer {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.sem-final-cta {
  text-align: center;
}

.sem-final-cta-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #FDD25E;
  color: #0F1A2A;
  padding: 24px 48px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.sem-final-cta-btn:hover {
  background: #ffffff;
  color: #0F1A2A;
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.sem-final-cta-note {
  margin-top: 32px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
}

/* SF-182 Section */
.sem-sf182 {
  padding: 48px 32px;
  background: var(--surface-container-low);
}

.sem-sf182-container {
  max-width: 1024px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.sem-sf182-content {
  background: white;
  padding: 64px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border-left: 8px solid var(--secondary);
}

.sem-sf182 .sem-eyebrow {
  color: #FDD25E;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #FDD25E;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-sf182-title {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-sf182-description {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--slate-600);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.sem-sf182-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--secondary);
  color: var(--on-secondary);
  padding: 20px 40px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-sf182-btn:hover {
  background: var(--secondary-container);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.sem-sf182-disclosure {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--slate-500);
  line-height: 1.5;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Training Details Section */
.sem-training-details {
  background: var(--secondary);
  color: var(--on-secondary);
  padding: 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin: 48px 0;
}

.sem-training-details .sem-eyebrow {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-training-details h3 {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.sem-training-details-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.sem-training-detail {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

.sem-training-detail-icon {
  font-size: 16px;
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sem-capacity-warning {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: 16px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 14px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Venue Links */
.sem-venue-links {
  margin-top: 32px;
  padding-top: 32px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-container-low);
}

.sem-venue-links h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-venue-links-grid {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.sem-venue-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: #16253C;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.sem-venue-link:hover {
  background: #57A5F4;
  color: #ffffff;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.sem-venue-link svg {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sem-parking-note {
  background: var(--surface);
  padding: 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-top: 32px;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
}

.sem-parking-note h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--secondary);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.sem-parking-note p {
  color: var(--slate-600);
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Registration Details */
.sem-registration-details {
  background: white;
  padding: 48px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin: 48px 0;
  border: 2px solid var(--surface-container-low);
}

.sem-registration-details .sem-eyebrow {
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sem-registration-details h3 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display), serif;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sem-registration-details-list {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
}

.sem-registration-detail {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
}

.sem-registration-detail-checkmark {
  color: var(--secondary);
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-top: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.sem-registration-detail-text {
  color: var(--slate-600);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* Mobile Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .sem-hero-content {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .sem-hero-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .sem-form-row {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .sem-curriculum-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  
  .sem-speaker-container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 48px;
  }
  
  .sem-speaker-image {
    max-width: 350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .sem-venue-content {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .sem-curriculum-card {
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  
  .sem-registration-form {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    margin: 0 16px;
  }
  
  .sem-trust-stats {
    gap: 32px;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .sem-training-details-grid,
  .sem-registration-details-list {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .sem-venue-links-grid {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .sem-hero-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
